title: It’s A Wembanyama World with Mark Schindler
itunes:title: It’s A Wembanyama World with Mark Schindler
description:
Miles and Jack were honored to be joined by the NBA and WNBA writer Mark Schindler on the latest episode. The trio discussed the state of the Pacers, some high expectations for a few surprise teams and the Wembanyama/Scoot showdown from Vegas.
